headline: 2 Oversold Stocks Set for a Comeback and 1 to Brush Off
summary: Rock-bottom prices don't always mean rock-bottom businesses. The stocks we're examining today have all touched their 52-week lows, creating a classic investor's dilemma: bargain opportunity or value trap?

headline: Paccar CFO to retire after 39 years
summary: Harrie Schippers will be succeeded by Brice Poplawski who will serve as SVP and CFO, effective June 2.
